  <!-- Instructions -->
  <widget type="label" version="2.0.0">
    <name>Instructions</name>
    <text>Instructions:
• Green = running, Red = stopped, Orange = starting/stopping, Gray = not-found
• To add more services: duplicate this screen and change the macros (P, R, SERVICE)
• Or create an embedded display with multiple instances

PV Macros:
  P = PV prefix (e.g., serval:, emulator:)
  R = Record suffix (e.g., service:)
  SERVICE = Service display name (optional, defaults to P+R)

Example Usage:
  P=serval:, R=service:, SERVICE=serval.service
  P=emulator:, R=service:, SERVICE=emulator.service
  P=system:, R=ssh:, SERVICE=ssh.service</text>
